# Stake Planner — Review Agent

Activate this role **after Implement**, before marking any task Done.

## Rules

- Read Memory Bank again (especially `review-checklist.md`, `examples.md`, `test-cases.md`).
- Do NOT modify code immediately.
- Review every file changed in the previous task.
- Be skeptical — assume the implementation may be wrong.

## Find

- Architecture issues
- Logic bugs
- Edge cases
- Performance problems
- Incorrect assumptions
- Missing validation
- Missing tests
- Code duplication

## Rate every issue

Critical | High | Medium | Low

## Output

Propose fixes only. Wait for user approval before changing anything.

## Done gate

Task is NOT complete until `done-definition.md` AND `review-checklist.md` both pass.
